íŸ@80111caba7446a169adf81959a698d0b6a2deb6a8bde0937b4625c5205d5f470⁄æTitle: title: history
Path: Examples
Content:
Get current history length
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> history | length


```
Show last 5 commands you have ran
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> history | last 5


```
Show last 5 commands with full details
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> history --long | last 5


```
Search all the commands from history that contains 'cargo'
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> history | where command =~ cargo | get command


```
